Body: It takes a long process for emeralds and the provision of after-sales service. Investors are going to pay high prices and it is very complex and risk associated to invest in emeralds without any proper knowledge. However, it is very difficult to invest in small and incomplete in emeralds. As a result, the lack of trust will be emeralds in the beginning.  Producers face some problems, as intermediates are involved in it. Therefore, they receive only 35% of the customer retail price. They face problems in expanding new markets. GEMERA's main aim is to create a modern and innovative opportunity that helps to solve all the problems in Colombian emerald's value chain. Therefore, with the help of blockchain technology, GEMERA is making easier to access and buying things, also helps in improving the emerald industry in a better way. GEMERA's offers crypto-tokens as back for 100% by Colombian emeralds and are going to redeem for each and every gemstone and stores like a trading token.  The project is going to introduce a marketplace that decentralizes with all the technologies to reveal all the information about the characteristics, the action or process, pictures and video of the emeralds. However, Germera connects both the investors and producers that help in accessing more easy, clear, democratic and available way to invest.
